---
// Portada profesional de Javiera Poblete Fernández
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Javiera Poblete Fernández | Docente de Lengua y Literatura</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Javiera Poblete Fernández - Docente de Lengua y Literatura, Postulante a Magíster en Educación Basado en Competencias, Universidad de Talca">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: ''Inter'', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 4rem 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '''';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: pulse 15s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
        }

        .profile-image {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .logo-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            position: relative;
            animation: floatLogo 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes floatLogo {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
        }

        .logo-circle-outer {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            animation: rotateOuter 20s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes rotateOuter {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .logo-circle-middle {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            animation: rotateMiddle 15s linear infinite reverse;
        }

        @keyframes rotateMiddle {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .logo-core {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #6366f1 50%, #ec4899 100%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.6),
                        inset 0 0 60px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: pulseGlow 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulseGlow {
            0%, 100% { 
                box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.6),
                            inset 0 0 60px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            }
            50% { 
                box-shadow: 0 25px 70px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.8),
                            inset 0 0 80px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            }
        }

        .logo-core::before {
            content: '''';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: linear-gradient(
                45deg,
                transparent,
                rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1),
                transparent
            );
            animation: shimmer 3s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes shimmer {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100%) translateY(-100%) rotate(45deg); }
            100% { transform: translateX(100%) translateY(100%) rotate(45deg); }
        }

        .logo-initials {
            font-family: ''Playfair Display'', serif;
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: scaleLetters 4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes scaleLetters {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
        }

        .logo-sparkles {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .sparkle {
            position: absolute;
            width: 4px;
            height: 4px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: sparkle 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .sparkle:nth-child(1) {
            top: 10%;
            left: 20%;
            animation-delay: 0s;
        }

        .sparkle:nth-child(2) {
            top: 80%;
            left: 30%;
            animation-delay: 1s;
        }

        .sparkle:nth-child(3) {
            top: 20%;
            right: 15%;
            animation-delay: 0.5s;
        }

        .sparkle:nth-child(4) {
            bottom: 15%;
            right: 25%;
            animation-delay: 1.5s;
        }

        .sparkle:nth-child(5) {
            top: 50%;
            left: 10%;
            animation-delay: 2s;
        }

        .sparkle:nth-child(6) {
            top: 30%;
            right: 10%;
            animation-delay: 2.5s;
        }

        @keyframes sparkle {
            0%, 100% { 
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0);
            }
            50% { 
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1.5);
            }
        }

        .logo-particles {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            overflow: visible;
        }

        .particle {
            position: absolute;
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: orbit 10s linear infinite;
        }

        .particle:nth-child(1) {
            animation-delay: 0s;
            animation-duration: 8s;
        }

        .particle:nth-child(2) {
            animation-delay: 2s;
            animation-duration: 10s;
        }

        .particle:nth-child(3) {
            animation-delay: 4s;
            animation-duration: 12s;
        }

        @keyframes orbit {
            from {
                transform: rotate(0deg) translateX(110px) rotate(0deg);
            }
            to {
                transform: rotate(360deg) translateX(110px) rotate(-360deg);
            }
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: ''Playfair Display'', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .institution {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            font-weight: 400;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 3rem;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: ''Playfair Display'', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.8rem;
        }

        .section-title i {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
            border-color: #667eea;
        }

        .card-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .card p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 1.2rem 3rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }

        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.05) 0%, rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.05) 100%);
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .subtitle {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .hero {
                padding: 3rem 2rem;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }

            .cards {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        .social-link {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .social-link:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <div class="profile-image">
                <div class="logo-container">
                    <div class="logo-circle-outer"></div>
                    <div class="logo-circle-middle"></div>
                    <div class="logo-core">
                        <div class="logo-initials">JP</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="logo-sparkles">
                        <div class="sparkle"></div>
                        <div class="sparkle"></div>
                        <div class="sparkle"></div>
                        <div class="sparkle"></div>
                        <div class="sparkle"></div>
                        <div class="sparkle"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="logo-particles">
                        <div class="particle"></div>
                        <div class="particle"></div>
                        <div class="particle"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h1>Javiera Poblete Fernández</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Docente de Lengua y Literatura</p>
            <p class="institution">Postulante a Magíster en Educación Basado en Competencias<br>Universidad de Talca</p>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#" class="social-link" title="LinkedIn">
                    <i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="mailto:javiera.poblete@ejemplo.cl" class="social-link" title="Email">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="social-link" title="GitHub">
                    <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
                    Formación Académica
                </h2>
                <div class="cards">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Lengua y Literatura</h3>
                        <p>Especialización en didáctica del lenguaje y literatura, con enfoque en competencias comunicativas y análisis textual.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Educación Basada en Competencias</h3>
                        <p>Formación de postgrado en metodologías innovadoras centradas en el desarrollo integral de habilidades.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-university"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Universidad de Talca</h3>
                        <p>Estudiante de Magíster comprometida con la excelencia educativa y la investigación pedagógica.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    <i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i>
                    Experiencia Docente
                </h2>
                <div class="cards">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Enseñanza Innovadora</h3>
                        <p>Desarrollo de estrategias pedagógicas que promueven el pensamiento crítico y la creatividad en el aula.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Evaluación por Competencias</h3>
                        <p>Implementación de sistemas de evaluación integral que miden el desarrollo de habilidades complejas.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Innovación Educativa</h3>
                        <p>Integración de tecnología y metodologías activas para potenciar el aprendizaje significativo.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <h2 class="section-title" style="justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    <i class="fas fa-laptop"></i>
                    Sistema de Gestión Académica
                </h2>
                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">
                    Accede al sistema integral de registro de notas y seguimiento del proceso educativo
                </p>
                <a href="/privado/?docente=javiera" class="cta-button">
                    <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>
                    Acceder al Sistema
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Javiera Poblete Fernández. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">Docente comprometida con la excelencia educativa</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
